{"tid":1950381,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"長江中心 交易廣場 上班族中招","createTime":"2020-03-30T09:53:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T11:39:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ef72b183b2ca9a211c344ec4eb18041ff195b9a4","tid":1950381,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T09:53:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200330/PAYEW6Q2BNGG4E22K2FVQBYJ7M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200330%2FPAYEW6Q2BNGG4E22K2FVQBYJ7M%2F&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2SIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=2c3f6cb8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200330%2FPAYEW6Q2BNGG4E22K2FVQBYJ7M%2F&h=b0f335ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200330/PAYEW6Q2BNGG4E22K2FVQBYJ7M/</a><br />\n<br />\n長江中心 交易廣場 上班族中招<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200330/large/1585498264_f686.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200330%2Flarge%2F1585498264_f686.gif&h=4c485f81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n長江中心有租戶職員確診。黃麗英攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】武漢肺炎殺入中環金融區，長江集團中心及交易廣場一座分別有租戶職員確診，大廈管理處已加強消毒。<br />\n<br />\n管理處加強消毒<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：武漢肺炎疫情最新發展<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n長江集團中心物業管理公司前日貼通告，指該中心39樓租戶一名職員對病毒檢測呈陽性，該確診職員對上一次進入辦公室時間為本月17日，管理公司因應情況已開始消毒，範圍包括確診職員所在及上下三層辦公樓層、地下大堂、廁所等。另外，管理公司亦呼籲所有租戶如有職員確診，應即時通報。<br />\n<br />\n據悉該確診的56歲男職員，上周三咳嗽及疲勞，前日確診。據衞生防護中心資料，該名確診者居住灣仔譚臣道117號至119號嘉易大廈，曾光顧酒吧Dusk Till Dawn。<br />\n<br />\n另外，香港置地日前亦向租戶發通告，證實交易廣場一座有第二名患者，涉及26樓租戶一名職員，上周四證實確診。該職員上次出入大廈是本月20日，管理公司事後加強消毒。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黃麗英"},{"pid":"18b76d23a16ef5042db474531c294c1079334518","tid":1950381,"uid":106290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T14:58:36.000Z","msg":"交易廣場中左幾個啦<br />\n17樓又好似有<br />\n上市party又有個中"},{"pid":"63a6aec3641a5c11f50431e25d7f62629dcbe8ca","tid":1950381,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T09:42:10.000Z","msg":"前幾日先去完<br />\n呢排有兩聲咳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ae9d2a040a3c31d4c4ddf2a47c2f99f0cd6acc","tid":1950381,"uid":128014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63a6aec3641a5c11f50431e25d7f62629dcbe8ca","tid":1950381,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T09:42:10.000Z","msg":"前幾日先去完<br />\n呢排有兩聲咳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T11:39:06.000Z","msg":"今日你係咪唔見咗銀包電話？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}